{"word":"μὴ 2","slug":"μὴ 2","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n67285\" key=\"mh\\2\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">μὴ γάρ</orth>, an elliptic phrase, freq. in emphatic denial, or in assenting to a denial or prohibition, etc., <sense id=\"n67285.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">certainly not</tr_>, where Verb in imper. or opt. must be supplied from the context, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μὴ λεγέτω τὸ ὄνομα</foreign>. . Answ. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μὴ γάρ [λεγέτω]</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg006.perseus-grc1:177e\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Tht.\">Tht.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">177e</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg007.perseus-grc1:255b\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Sph.\">Sph.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">255b</biblScope> </bibl>: not in a reply, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μὴ γὰρ δὴ δίναν γ᾽ Εὐρώτα</foreign> (sc. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἔλθοιμι</foreign>) <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg011.perseus-grc1:210\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Tr.\">Tr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">210</biblScope> </bibl> (lyr.): in parenthesis, where it may be translated <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">much less</tr_> (cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μὴ ὅτι</foreign>), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0026.tlg002.perseus-grc1:158\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aeschin.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.158</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">μὴ γὰρ τῆς πόλεώς γε μηδ᾽ ἐμοῦ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg018.perseus-grc1:200\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.200</biblScope></bibl></cit>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}